      A desktop home<br />for your coding agents.
    </h1>

    <p class="subhead">
      Dynamo runs Codex, Claude, Cursor, and OpenCode side&#8209;by&#8209;side —
      with shared threads, isolated worktrees, and a coordinator that picks the
      right model for each task.
    </p>

    <div class="cta-row">
